<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>A Note About Your Upcoming Service — {{year}} {{make}} {{model}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
        <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center;">
              {{#if dealershipLogo}}
              <img src="{{dealershipLogo}}" alt="{{dealershipName}}" style="max-height: 60px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              {{else}}
              <h2 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">{{dealershipName}}</h2>
              {{/if}}
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Hero Banner -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: {{brandSecondaryColor}}; padding: 25px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 26px; line-height: 1.3;">Something to Consider Before Your Service Visit</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Main Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},
              </p>
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                While your <strong>{{year}} {{make}} {{model}} {{trim}}</strong> is in for service, we wanted to share something worth considering. Your vehicle currently holds strong market value, and depending on the nature of your visit, now could be an ideal time to explore a trade-in.
              </p>

              <!-- Service Date Callout -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 25px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #fafafa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px;">
                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td width="60" valign="middle" style="padding-right: 15px;">
                          <div style="width: 50px; height: 50px; background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center; line-height: 50px;">
                            <span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 24px;">&#128295;</span>
                          </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="middle">
                          <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 3px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Upcoming Service Appointment</p>
                          <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">{{serviceDate}}</p>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Why Consider Trading -->
              <h2 style="color: #333333; font-size: 18px; margin: 30px 0 15px;">Why Consider Trading Now?</h2>

              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 12px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="30" valign="top" style="padding-top: 2px;">
                    <div style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; border-radius: 50%; margin-top: 6px;"></div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;"><strong>Strong market demand</strong> — Pre-owned vehicles like yours are in high demand, which keeps trade-in values elevated.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 12px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="30" valign="top" style="padding-top: 2px;">
                    <div style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; border-radius: 50%; margin-top: 6px;"></div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;"><strong>Avoid future repair costs</strong> — If your service visit involves aging components, trading now lets you skip those expenses entirely.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 12px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="30" valign="top" style="padding-top: 2px;">
                    <div style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; border-radius: 50%; margin-top: 6px;"></div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;"><strong>Seamless transition</strong> — Since you are already visiting us, we can appraise your vehicle on the spot and have you driving something new the same day.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 25px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="30" valign="top" style="padding-top: 2px;">
                    <div style="width: 8px; height: 8px; background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; border-radius: 50%; margin-top: 6px;"></div>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.5; margin: 0;"><strong>Latest safety and technology</strong> — Newer models come with advanced driver-assist features, improved efficiency, and full warranty protection.</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Reassurance Note -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 0 0 25px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #f5f5f5; border-left: 4px solid {{brandPrimaryColor}}; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; padding: 18px 22px;">
                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
                      <strong>No pressure, just information.</strong> We are happy to service your current vehicle regardless. But if you have been thinking about an upgrade, your service visit is a convenient time to explore that option.
                    </p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 30px;">
                When you arrive for your appointment, let your service advisor know if you would like a complimentary trade-in appraisal. There is no obligation — just an opportunity to see what is possible.
              </p>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{dealershipWebsite}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 6px;">
                      Browse New Inventory
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0 0;">
                Questions? Call us at <a href="tel:{{dealershipPhone}}" style="color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold;">{{dealershipPhone}}</a>
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #333333; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <p style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0 0 5px;">{{dealershipName}}</p>
              <p style="color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 5px;">
                <a href="tel:{{dealershipPhone}}" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">{{dealershipPhone}}</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 15px;">
                <a href="{{dealershipWebsite}}" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">{{dealershipWebsite}}</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #777777; font-size: 11px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;">
                Trade-in values are estimates and subject to in-person vehicle inspection and appraisal.
                If you no longer wish to receive these emails, please contact us to opt out.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
